{{vgname|奇異人生：本色|en=Life Is Strange: True Colors}}是由[[Deck_Nine|Deck Nine]]开发、[[史克威尔艾尼克斯|史克威尔艾尼克斯]]之[[史克威尔艾尼克斯欧洲|欧洲子公司]]发行的[[冒险游戏|冒险游戏]]，于2021年9月10日在[[Microsoft_Windows|Microsoft Windows]]、[[PlayStation_4|PlayStation 4]]、[[PlayStation_5|PlayStation 5]]、[[Xbox_One|Xbox One]]、[[Xbox_Series_X/S|Xbox Series X/S]]和[[Google_Stadia|Stadia]]发行。本作是[[奇异人生|《奇异人生》]]系列的第五部作品，也是继《[[奇异人生2|奇异人生2]]》之后的第三部主线游戏。本作讲述具有同理心超能力的年轻女子Alex Chen发掘她兄弟死亡真相的故事。

== 玩法 ==
《奇異人生：本色》是第三人称视角的[[冒险游戏|冒险游戏]]，玩家将探索虚构的Haven Springs，通过[[对话树|对话树]]系统与[[非玩家角色|非玩家角色]]进行对话。

== 剧情 ==
Alex Chen是一位年轻的亚裔美国女性，在寄养家庭中长大，过着一段并不平静的童年。八年后，在兄弟Gabe的鼓励下，Alex回家团聚。Gabe后来死于一次神秘的事故。Alex具有同理心超能力，能够吸收並操控他人強烈的情緒，代价是会被他人的情绪“感染”。她将利用这一超能力调查出事故背后的真相。一路上，Alex将在[[科羅拉多州|科罗拉多州]]风景如画的山镇Haven Springs遇到许多人，包括《[[奇异人生：暴风前夕|暴风前夕]]》中的Ryan和Steph。<ref name="IGN">{{Cite web|title=Life Is Strange: True Colors Coming in September, No Episodic Release|url=https://www.ign.com/articles/life-is-strange-true-colors-release-date-september-no-episodes|accessdate=2021-03-18|author=Skrebels|date=2021-03-18|first=Joe|work=IGN|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20210318180441/https://www.ign.com/articles/life-is-strange-true-colors-release-date-september-no-episodes|archivedate=2021-03-18|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="Polygon music">{{Cite web|title=Life is Strange: True Colors stars an Asian American lead in an all-new adventure|url=https://www.polygon.com/2021/3/18/22334256/life-is-strange-true-colors-release-date-mxmtoon|author=McWhertor|date=2021-03-18|first=Michael|work=Polygon|language=en|access-date=2021-03-22|archive-date=2021-06-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210603183532/https://www.polygon.com/2021/3/18/22334256/life-is-strange-true-colors-release-date-mxmtoon|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=Life is Strange 3 drops this September|url=https://www.pcgamesn.com/life-is-strange-true-colors/release-date|work=PCGamesN|access-date=2021-03-22|archive-date=2021-06-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210613210652/https://www.pcgamesn.com/life-is-strange-true-colors/release-date|dead-url=no}}</ref>

== 制作 ==
曾开发《[[奇异人生：暴风前夕|暴风前夕]]》的Deck Nine于2017年开始开发《本色》。<ref name="eurogamer announce">{{Cite web|title=Life is Strange: True Colors is a gorgeous new chapter which ditches the series' episodic model|url=https://www.eurogamer.net/articles/2020-03-18-life-is-strange-true-colors-is-a-gorgeous-new-chapter-which-ditches-the-series-episodic-model|accessdate=2021-03-19|author=Phillips|date=2021-03-18|first=Tom|work=[[Eurogamer|Eurogamer]]|archive-date=2021-04-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210422083644/https://www.eurogamer.net/articles/2020-03-18-life-is-strange-true-colors-is-a-gorgeous-new-chapter-which-ditches-the-series-episodic-model|dead-url=no}}</ref>2021年3月18日，Square Enix发布了《本色》的预告片，同时宣布《[[奇异人生|奇异人生]]》和《暴风前夕》的重制版将于2021年晚些时候发行。<ref>{{Cite web|title=Square Enix will debut the next Life is Strange game on March 18th|url=https://www.engadget.com/square-enix-life-is-strange-march-18th-174710906.html|accessdate=2021-03-12|work=Engadget|language=en-US|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20210312004447/https://www.engadget.com/square-enix-life-is-strange-march-18th-174710906.html|archivedate=2021-03-12|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=Square Enix showing off new Life is Strange next week as part of spring showcase|url=https://www.eurogamer.net/articles/2021-03-11-square-enix-showing-off-new-life-is-strange-next-week-as-part-of-spring-showcase|accessdate=2021-03-12|author=Wales|date=2021-03-11|first=Matt|work=Eurogamer|language=en|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20210311180407/https://www.eurogamer.net/articles/2021-03-11-square-enix-showing-off-new-life-is-strange-next-week-as-part-of-spring-showcase|archivedate=2021-03-11|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=Square Enix to reveal new Life Is Strange and more in March 18 livestream|url=https://www.polygon.com/2021/3/11/22325387/square-enix-presents-march-2021-life-is-strange-avengers-outriders-tomb-raider|accessdate=2021-03-12|author=McWhertor|date=2021-03-11|first=Michael|work=Polygon|language=en|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20210311171435/https://www.polygon.com/2021/3/11/22325387/square-enix-presents-march-2021-life-is-strange-avengers-outriders-tomb-raider|archivedate=2021-03-11|dead-url=no}}</ref>

== 发行 ==
《本色》计划于2021年9月10日在[[Microsoft_Windows|Microsoft Windows]]、[[PlayStation_4|PlayStation 4]]、[[PlayStation_5|PlayStation 5]]、[[Xbox_One|Xbox One]]、[[Xbox_Series_X/S|Xbox Series X/S]]和[[Google_Stadia|Stadia]]发行。《奇异人生》系列前作都有固定的发行时间表，但《本色》的五个章节将一次性发行。<ref name="eurogamer announce" />《本色》另有豪華版提供，内有獨家額外劇情〈波長〉，玩家将扮演Steph<ref name="Polygon music" />。《本色》終極版组合包还包含《奇异人生》原作和《暴风前夕》的重制版。

== 争议 ==
2021年9月10日，《奇異人生：本色》在[[Steam|Steam]]发售后，因游戏宣传材料中出现象徵[[西藏独立运动|西藏獨立運動]]的[[雪山獅子旗|雪山獅子旗]]，引发中国大陆的玩家不滿，并遭到[[評論轟炸|差评轰炸]]<ref>[https://www.pcgamer.com/chinese-players-start-review-bombing-life-is-strange-true-colors-over-tibetan-flag/ Chinese players start review-bombing Life is Strange: True Colors over Tibetan flag] {{Wayback|url=https://www.pcgamer.com/chinese-players-start-review-bombing-life-is-strange-true-colors-over-tibetan-flag/ |date=20210914072629 }}.PC Gamer.2021-09-11.[2021-09-19].</ref><ref name=":0">{{Cite web|title=游戏《奇异人生：本色》出现“藏独”旗帜，中国玩家差评抵制|url=https://www.guancha.cn/culture/2021_09_10_606674.shtml|access-date=2021-10-12|author=张照栋|date=2021-09-10|publisher=观察者网|language=zh|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211012100837/https://www.guancha.cn/culture/2021_09_10_606674.shtml|archive-date=2021-10-12|dead-url=no}}</ref>。发售当日受此影响，该游戏在steam平台上的中文测评显示“多半差评”<ref name=":0" />。本游戏在中国大陆地区的Steam商店页面在9月11日后处于下架状态<ref>{{cite news |author=劉法柔 |title=遊戲驚現藏獨旗幟！中國小粉紅痛批話題新作辱華 |url=https://newtalk.tw/news/view/2021-09-11/634752 |work=[[新頭殼|新頭殼]] |date=2021-09-11 |access-date=2021-09-18 |language=zh-tw |archive-date=2021-09-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210918150812/https://newtalk.tw/news/view/2021-09-11/634752 }}</ref>。

